                                bệnh.</p>
                            <p class="m-0">Đọc kỹ hướng dẫn sử dụng trước khi dùng.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="d-flex align-items-center mb-4 gap-3">
                        <label class="text-muted mb-0">Chọn số lượng</label>
                        <div
                            class="quantity-input d-flex align-items-center border rounded-pill px-3 py-2 bg-light shadow-sm">
                            <button class="btn btn-link text-dark px-2 py-0 fs-5" onclick="decreaseQuantity()"
                                style="outline:none;"><i class="fas fa-minus"></i></button>
                            <input type="number" id="quantity" class="form-control text-center border-0 bg-light mx-2"
                                value="1" min="1" max="@Model.StockQuantity" readonly
                                style="width: 60px; font-size: 1.1rem;" />
                            <button class="btn btn-link text-dark px-2 py-0 fs-5" onclick="increaseQuantity()"
                                style="outline:none;"><i class="fas fa-plus"></i></button>
                        </div>
                    </div>
